"use strict";(self.webpackChunkxifan_blog=self.webpackChunkxifan_blog||[]).push([[4161],{3979:(e,i,n)=>{n.r(i),n.d(i,{comp:()=>t,data:()=>d});var s=n(641);const a=[(0,s.Fv)('<h2 id="前言" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#前言"><span>前言</span></a></h2><p>首先说下背景，在本机同时使用了Github和Gitlab，对应个人和公司使用；不太想使用同一个SSH密钥，就创建了两个SSH密钥。</p><h2 id="正文" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#正文"><span>正文</span></a></h2><p>首先，在.ssh目录创建config文件；在<code>~/.ssh/config</code>文件中，指定不同的SSH密钥，Git会根据HostName自动选择正确的密钥进行连接。</p><div class="language-plaintext line-numbers-mode" data-ext="plaintext" data-title="plaintext"><pre class="language-plaintext"><code># 配置第一个仓库的 SSH 密钥\nHost github.com\n  HostName github.com\n  User git\n  IdentityFile ~/.ssh/id_rsa_repo1\n  IdentitiesOnly yes\n\n# 配置第二个仓库的 SSH 密钥\nHost gitLab.com-repo2\n  HostName gitLab.com\n  User git\n  IdentityFile ~/.ssh/id_rsa_repo2\n  IdentitiesOnly yes\n\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><ul><li><code>Host</code> 是你给每个配置设置的别名。</li><li><code>HostName</code> 是实际的 GitHub 地址（github.com）。</li><li><code>IdentityFile</code> 指定你希望为该主机使用的 SSH 密钥。</li></ul><p>现在，使用你在配置文件中设置的别名来进行<code>git clone</code>：</p><div class="language-bash line-numbers-mode" data-ext="sh" data-title="sh"><pre class="language-bash"><code><span class="token function">git</span> clone git@github.com:username/repo1.git\n\n<span class="token comment"># 如果别名设置的是githubAlias，则使用下面的命令：</span>\n<span class="token function">git</span> clone git@githubAlias:username/repo1.git\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div>',8)],l={},t=(0,n(6262).A)(l,[["render",function(e,i){return(0,s.uX)(),(0,s.CE)("div",null,a)}]]),d=JSON.parse('{"path":"/blogs/note/gongchenghua/GitshiyongzhidingdeSSHmiyuejinxinglianjie.html","title":"Git使用指定的SSH密钥进行连接","lang":"en-US","frontmatter":{"title":"Git使用指定的SSH密钥进行连接","date":"2025-01-16T00:00:00.000Z","categories":["note"],"tags":["前端工程化"]},"headers":[{"level":2,"title":"前言","slug":"前言","link":"#前言","children":[]},{"level":2,"title":"正文","slug":"正文","link":"#正文","children":[]}],"git":{"createdTime":1737108179000,"updatedTime":1737108179000,"contributors":[{"name":"稀饭","email":"lixifan@ane56.com","commits":1}]},"filePathRelative":"blogs/note/工程化/Git使用指定的SSH密钥进行连接.md"}')}}]);